U||He went away in a very gloomy frame of mind.
U||On the morrow,‚Äîfor he only existed from morrow to morrow, there was, so to speak, no to-day for him,‚Äîon the morrow, he found no one at the Luxembourg; he had expected this. At dusk, he went to the house.
